suits.Name: Ninja
suits.Description: The Ninja exosuit is Banzai Squadron's quick strike specialist.

suits.Name: Tempest
suits.Description: The Tempest exosuit is a balanced fighter for Banzai Squadron.

suits.Name: Dragon
suits.Description: The Dragon exosuit is Banzai Squadron's heavy hitter.

suits.Name: Finn
suits.Description: The quick and nimble Finn exosuit is an adventurer's dream.

suits.Name: Marceline
suits.Description: Unmatched in speed and agility, the Marceline exosuit is extremely mobile.

suits.Name: Rex
suits.Description: The Generator Rex exosuit's high Tech factor lets it access boosts and heavy weapons quickly.

suits.Name: Ult. Big Chill
suits.Description: The Ultimate Big Chill exosuit is ready to burn through the competition.

suits.Name: Mordecai & Rigby
suits.Description: The Mordecai & Rigby exosuit is inspired by both stars of Regular Show.

suits.Name: Manus
suits.Description: This exosuit is inspired by Lance's armored form, Manus.

suits.Name: Ult. Echo Echo
suits.Description: The Ultimate Echo Echo exosuit is a sound overall fighter.

suits.Name: Bobo
suits.Description: The Bobo exosuit's high tech factor lets it grab boosts and heavy weapons quickly.

suits.Name: Flapjack
suits.Description: The Flapjack exosuit zips around the battlefield with speed and agility.

suits.Name: Johnny Test
suits.Description: The Johnny Test exosuit has been Johnny tested for quality assurance.

suits.Name: Ult. Swampfire
suits.Description: The Ultimate Swampfire exosuit features some solid firepower.

suits.Name: Biowulf
suits.Description: Boasting great strength and speed, the Biowulf exosuit is a powerful fighter.

suits.Name: Corus
suits.Description: This exosuit is based on Ilana's armored form, Corus.

suits.Name: Ice King
suits.Description: Specializing in sub-zero temperatures, the Ice King exosuit is a hardy fighter.

suits.Name: Heatblast
suits.Description: The battle always heats up when the Heatblast exosuit is on the scene.

suits.Name: PPG Suit
suits.Description: The Powerpuff Girls exosuit can speed around the battlefield and chase down the enemy.

suits.Name: SamJack
suits.Description: The Samurai Jack exosuit is a focused fighter that likes being in the middle of the action.

suits.Name: Phantom
suits.Description: The Phantom exosuit is Atlas Brigade's equivalent of a super spy.

suits.Name: Sentinel
suits.Description: The Sentinel exosuit is a well-rounded unit that Atlas Brigade can always depend on.

suits.Name: Behemoth
suits.Description: When the Atlas Brigade needs brute strength, it calls in the Behemoth.

suits.Name: Ult. Humungousaur
suits.Description: The Ultimate Humungousaur exosuit is a tough, strong fighter.

suits.Name: Gwen
suits.Description: The Gwen exosuit relies on speed and evasion to take down the enemy.

suits.Name: Jake
suits.Description: The Jake exosuit is a flexible fighter that shifts easily between offensive and defensive tactics.

suits.Name: Van Kleiss
suits.Description: The Van Kleiss exosuit specializes in both speed and precision.

suits.Name: NRG
suits.Description: The NRG exosuit makes up for its lack of speed with exceptional toughness.

suits.Name: Rath
suits.Description: Built for pure offense, the Rath exosuit is like a force of nature.

suits.Name: Skalamander
suits.Description: Tough and relentless, the Skalamander exosuit is good for stalking opponents.

suits.Name: Chowder
suits.Description: The Chowder exosuit is a hardy fighter with a hunger for mayhem.

suits.Name: Mojo Jojo
suits.Description: The Mojo Jojo exosuit always has a brilliant plan in the works.

suits.Name: Bling Bling Boy
suits.Description: The Bling Bling Boy exosuit has tech expertise that lets it grab boosts and heavy weapons quickly.

suits.Name: Fourarms
suits.Description: The Four Arms exosuit is a heavy hitter built for brawling.

suits.Name: Agent Six
suits.Description: The Agent Six exosuit is inspired by the sixth most dangerous person on the planet.

suits.Name: Princess Bubblegum
suits.Description: It may look sweet, but the Princess Bubblegum exosuit can really mess up its opponents.

suits.Name: Ult. Cannonbolt
suits.Description: The Ultimate Cannonbolt exosuit uses highly durable shields without sacrificing speed.

suits.Name: Grim
suits.Description: The Grim exosuit is inspired by the power of the Underworld.

suits.Name: Dexter
suits.Description: Thanks to its high Tech factor, the Dexter exosuit can pick up boosts and heavy weapons quickly.

suits.Name: Vilgax
suits.Description: The Vilgax exosuit is a hard-hitting bruiser with plenty of offensive power.

suits.Name: Darwin
suits.Description: Speedy and lightweight, the Darwin exosuit is always ready to jump into action.

suits.Name: Gumball
suits.Description: Fast and frenetic, the Gumball exosuit thrives on chaos, running straight into the middle of battle.

suits.Name: Lumpy Space Princess
suits.Description: The Lumpy Space Princess exosuit is so tough that attacks just roll off it like, "Whatever!"

suits.Name: Beemo
suits.Description: Camera, game system, tech expertise, and supercharged pistol--the Beemo exosuit has it all!

suits.Name: Ultimate Kevin
suits.Description: Combining aspects of many Omnitrix aliens, the Ultimate Kevin exosuit is tough to take down.

suits.Name: Alien X
suits.Description: Using a mastery of reality, the Alien X exosuit can do big damage from a long distance.

suits.Name: Rigby
suits.Description: With high speed and regen, the Rigby exosuit is a quick and versatile attacker.

suits.Name: Skips
suits.Description: The Skips exosuit is designed to achieve maximum mobility by skipping.

suits.Name: Tina
suits.Description: It may not be the fastest or most agile suit, but the Tina exosuit is as tough as they come.

suits.Name: Penny
suits.Description: The Penny exosuit is fast and smart, with a high Tech factor for boosts and weapons.

suits.Name: Ben 10 Atlas
suits.Description: The Ben 10 Atlas is the original prototype exosuit, outfitted and optimized for Atlas Brigade.

suits.Name: Ben 10 Banzai
suits.Description: The Ben 10 Banzai is the original prototype exosuit, outfitted and optimized for Banzai Squadron.

suits.Name: Elite Marceline
suits.Description: The gold-plated Elite Marceline exosuit is as fast as ever, but now has a scary long-distance game.

suits.Name: Elite Manus
suits.Description: The gold-plated Elite Manus exosuit has a higher speed and an unstoppable close attack.

suits.Name: Elite Rath
suits.Description: The gold-plated Elite Rath exosuit has a massive shield upgrade and can hit hard from farther away.

suits.Name: Elite Mojo Jojo
suits.Description: The gold-plated Elite Mojo Jojo exosuit has an even higher Tech factor and a quick burst attack.

weapons.Name: Bulldog
weapons.Description: Every exosuit uses the Bulldog energy pistol as a backup sidearm because it never runs out of ammo.

weapons.Name: Marksman
weapons.Description: The Marksman specializes in taking down single opponents from long range.

weapons.Name: Ballista
weapons.Description: When the short range Ballista scores a hit, it can devastate nearby opponents.

weapons.Name: Wildfire
weapons.Description: The Wildfire sprays so many shots so quickly it can overwhelm unsuspecting enemies.

weapons.Name: Tridex
weapons.Description: Featuring a balance of damage, range and speed, the Tridex fires three shots in a wide angle.

weapons.Name: Helix Cannon
weapons.Description: The Helix Cannon launches Helix Grenades with great range and accuracy.

weapons.Name: Longshot
weapons.Description: The Longshot can zoom in on enemies and deal heavy damage from a safe distance.

weapons.Name: Rocket Pod
weapons.Description: The Rocket Pod can sway the tide of battle with its massive explosions.

weapons.Name: Helix Grenade
weapons.Description: All exosuits can throw Helix Grenades, compact spheres that explode in a burst of Helix energy.

mods.Description: No Description

mods.Name: Shuriken Shot
mods.Description: Based on the efficiency of ancient thrown weapons, this mod give the Wildfire bigger clips and shorter reload times.

mods.Name: Hailstorm Clips
mods.Description: Doubling the clip size means half as many reloads, making it easier to fill the map with a hailstorm of Tridex shots.

mods.Name: Fangs of Fury
mods.Description: With a faster rate of fire and longer range, this mod adds even more "bite" to the already intimidating Marksman.

mods.Name: Mathematical!
mods.Description: This totally algebraic mod multiplies the projectiles in the Tridex, making it fire five shots instead of just three.

mods.Name: Rock Out!
mods.Description: The Wildfire really rocks with this mod, which pushes its rate of fire through the roof while also improving accuracy.

mods.Name: Punkbuster
mods.Description: Give the Ballista more solid footing with better accuracy and rate of fire when this mod is equipped.

mods.Name: Supercooling
mods.Description: Chilling its propulsion system to subzero temperatures lets the Tridex fire faster and with more accuracy.

mods.Name: The Hammer
mods.Description: This mod beefs up the Wildfire's range and clip size, allowing it to hammer opponents from farther away.

mods.Name: Supreme Weapon
mods.Description: Based on Galaluna technology, this mod enhances nearly every aspect of the Wildfire, from range to clip size to accuracy.

mods.Name: Wave Amplifier
mods.Description: Charging its trigger mechanism with sonic energy gives the Marksman a faster firing rate to keep enemies at bay.

mods.Name: Double Trouble
mods.Description: Equipped with this mod, the Bulldog becomes twice as dangerous, firing two projectiles in each shot.

mods.Name: Sugar Rush
mods.Description: Adding a delicious candy coating to its power core gives the Tridex a manic boost in speed, making it fire much faster than usual.

mods.Name: Johnny X-treme
mods.Description: Fueled by the superpowered essence of Johnny X, this mod gives the Wildfire extremely long range.

mods.Name: Fired Up
mods.Description: This mod superheats the Marksman's ammo, which reduces it to 3 shots per clip but greatly increases its range, damage and speed.

mods.Name: Lightning Reflexes
mods.Description: Fine-tuning the Ballista's trigger mechanism gives this powerful weapon an inhumanly fast rate of fire.

mods.Name: Target Lock
mods.Description: By dedicating a separate processor to targeting, the Wildfire achieves much greater accuracy and slightly more damage.

mods.Name: Deep Freeze
mods.Description: Coating its ammo in ice allows the Tridex to fire a tighter spread of shots with more accuracy and more concentrated damage.

mods.Name: Arc Furnace
mods.Description: This mod is designed to build up extreme heat within the Marksman, resulting in slow but extremely damaging shots.

mods.Name: Sugar & Spice
mods.Description: With a dash of sugar and spice, this mod gives the Ballista greater accuracy and lets it dish out two quick doses of damage.

mods.Name: Samurai Swiftness
mods.Description: Infused with the swiftness of a samurai, the Bulldog pistol gets a faster rate of fire and lightning-quick reloads.

mods.Name: Hair Trigger
mods.Description: This mod increases the sensitivity of the Marksman's trigger interface, allowing it to fire repeatedly at a faster rate.

mods.Name: Focused Fire
mods.Description: By adjusting the barrels of the Tridex, this mod narrows the angle between its three shots, focusing more damage in a smaller area.

mods.Name: Kinetic Accelerator
mods.Description: Directing more kinetic energy to the propulsion system adds extra range to the Ballista's barrage of shots.

mods.Name: Humungous Core
mods.Description: Enlarging the energy core to humungous proportions allows the Tridex to fire five shots instead of just three.

mods.Name: Keystone of Bezel
mods.Description: Like its namesake, this mod enhances existing strengths, making the already fast Wildfire even faster and doubling its shots.

mods.Name: Bazooka Goblin
mods.Description: Harnessing the power of an imaginary bazooka goblin, this mod lets the Ballista fire two powerful shots in quick succession.

mods.Name: Nanite Control
mods.Description: Accuracy is normally one of the Wildfire's weakest points, but this mod infuses every shot with nanites, allowing for much greater precision.

mods.Name: Nuclear Fission
mods.Description: This mod causes a fission reaction in the Marksman that enlarges its ammo clips. The resulting energy also propels shots farther.

mods.Name: Power Slam
mods.Description: Adding even more power to the already damaging Ballista results in a wider shot with more projectiles slamming into the opponent.

mods.Name: Crystal Prism
mods.Description: By focusing energy through a crystal prism, this mod gives the Ballista greater range and faster rate of fire.

mods.Name: Smorgasbord
mods.Description: The Tridex can serve up a smorgasbord of destruction with this mod that gives it an extra projectile and a faster rate of fire.

mods.Name: Chemical X
mods.Description: A dash of Chemical X in this mod gives the Tridex a faster firing rate and extremely long range.

mods.Name: Secret Weapon
mods.Description: This modded Bulldog energy pistol has greater range than usual, giving it a hidden advantage over other pistols.

mods.Name: Punch It!
mods.Description: This mod amps up the Ballista's speed, allowing it to punch through opponents with ease.

mods.Name: Bleach Protocol
mods.Description: Using Providence's "bleach" technology, this mod gives the Wildfire powerful 5-shot bursts that can wipe opponents off the map.

mods.Name: Jawbreaker
mods.Description: This sugary mod hypes up the Marksman's power to the extreme, making it so immensely damaging it requires a reload after each shot.

mods.Name: Hand Cannon
mods.Description: By rapidly spinning the energy core, this mod turns the Bulldog pistol into a mini-Ballista, allowing it to fire a quick 5-shot spread.

mods.Name: Underworld Overload
mods.Description: With this mod, the Wildfire can summon more ammo into each clip, meaning fewer reloads and more action.

mods.Name: Infinite Loop
mods.Description: This mod uses shrink rays to fit an entire ammo supply in a single clip, meaning the Tridex can fire all its ammo without ever reloading.

mods.Name: Chimera Strike
mods.Description: The alien technology in this mod makes the Marksman twice as threatening by giving it two projectiles instead of just one.

mods.Name: Overgill
mods.Description: By cramming all your ammo into one clip, this fishy mod makes sure you're never caught reloading your Marksman.

mods.Name: Wild Child
mods.Description: Mirroring Gumball's enthusiasm, this mod makes the Wildfire even wilder, hitting anything and everything that gets in its way.

mods.Name: Lump Off!
mods.Description: Driven by the power of sheer disdain, this mod launches Wildfire shots farther than usual. Like, totally far.

mods.Name: Cheat Code
mods.Description: Powered by Beemo's main brain game frame, this mod gives the Bulldog energy pistol extreme range.

mods.Name: Osmosian Overload
mods.Description: This mod fuses multiple alien DNA patterns into the Ballista, making it into an even more efficient weapon of destruction.

mods.Name: Celestial Warp
mods.Description: By slightly warping the time-space continuum, this mod increases the Marksman's range and damage.

mods.Name: In Your Face!
mods.Description: This mod takes the wide-range Tridex and amps up its firing speed to hyperactive levels.

mods.Name: Fist of Justice
mods.Description: As powerful as an immortal yeti, this mod lets you dish out justice with a mighty double blast from your Ballista.

mods.Name: Thunder Lizard
mods.Description: What's that thundering noise? It's a Marksman with this long-range mod hitting you from all the way across the map.

mods.Name: Pom Pom Power
mods.Description: Harnessing the energy of school spirit, this mod gives the Bulldog a double shot of cheerleading power.

mods.Name: Wildfire 2.0
mods.Description: This mod uses the Wildfire's original prototype model but boosts its performance across the board.

mods.Name: Tridex Max
mods.Description: This mod uses the Tridex's original prototype but combines all its ammo into a single, massive clip.

mods.Name: Bitemark II
mods.Description: This mod splits the Marksman's long-range shot in two, leaving victims with a double impact mark like a vampire bite.

mods.Name: Lance Charge
mods.Description: By concentrating its entire clip into just one shot, this mod turns the Bulldog into an ultra-damaging short-range 'lance' attack.

mods.Name: Tiger Strike
mods.Description: With this mod equipped, the Tridex can strike from farther away, giving it even better control over a wider area.

mods.Name: Mad Genius
mods.Description: By merging the qualities of a Bulldog and a Wildfire, this mod creates a Bulldog pistol with rapid bursts of explosive damage.
